      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-tier condition. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that remains in peak operating specification. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag six-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels through an M Variable Differential Lock. This example has undergone a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS overhaul to ensure mechanical longevity. The chassis exhibits zero flex, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory tolerances. Finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather, the aesthetic condition matches the mechanical excellence. A rare opportunity to own a high-revving icon with a documented service history.",
