      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I'm a bit sad to see this beauty go, but it's time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels basically brand new without the massive dealership sticker shock, this is the one. Come take a look and see for yourself, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
